attributes.review:
i downloaded the app because I wanted to see Trump’s ideas? (etc.) but the app is generally not great. Crashed my iPhone (though my phone is a tad old, it never acted this way before) and now it crashes every ~30 minutes. Genuinely do not recommend this app.

And as for the whole TikTok thing? Never used it, so I don’t care about it’s ban, but why exactly would you be against it if you’re not doing anything wrong?
